notes: JSON is text, written with JavaScript object notation.
JSON is a syntax for storing and exchanging data.
JSON files cannot have comments. Write any notes in this array.
A JSON document always starts with either an array [] or an object {}
Commas go between values in objects and arrays, not necessarily at the end of lines.
Object property names must be inside quotation marks.
String quotation marks must be double quotes, not single quotes.
